          content: "Certain warning signs suggest a particular Medicare Advantage plan may not serve you well. First, check whether your current doctors are in-network. Call their offices directly; don't rely solely on the plan\'s website directory, as these are often outdated. If most of your providers are out-of-network, avoid that plan unless you\'re willing to switch doctors.",
